      <title>马克龙任命国家银行 CDC 的伦巴第财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/macron-appoints-eric-lombard-as-french-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命埃里克·隆巴德为法国财政部长，新内阁中任命了一位经验丰富的金融专业人士，两位前总理也重返政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/macron-appoints-eric-lombard-as-french-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 17:47:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克执政党“矮子”宣布当选总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/mozambique-ruling-party-s-chapo-elected-president-judge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克最高选举法院在 10 月 9 日存在争议的选举中宣布执政党的丹尼尔·查波为当选总统，这一举动在该东南部非洲国家经历数周致命骚乱之后引发了新一轮抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/mozambique-ruling-party-s-chapo-elected-president-judge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 15:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登利用赦免权减免 37 项死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-commutes-37-death-sentences-in-latest-use-of-pardon-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周一减轻 37 名联邦囚犯的死刑，利用其总统赦免权将他们的刑期减为终身监禁，不得假释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-commutes-37-death-sentences-in-latest-use-of-pardon-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
